FOOT AND MOUTH DISEASE - ISRAEL, PALESTINIAN AUTHORITY: SEROTYPE O, GENOTYPING, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
*******************************************************************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
